<section id="how-it-works" class="hiw">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">How It Works</div>
    <h2 class="section-h">Three steps to permanent title protection.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">ProtectReal makes on-chain title registration as simple as checking your credit score — no technical knowledge required.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5S10.62 6.5 12 6.5s2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Verify Your Property</h3>
        <p>Enter your property address. We cross-reference public records, county deed data, and existing on-chain registries to establish a verified baseline.</p>
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 8h-1V6c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5S7 3.24 7 6v2H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V10c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6 9c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2s.9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2-.9 2-2 2zm3.1-9H8.9V6c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1 1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1v2z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Mint Your NFTitle</h3>
        <p>Your title is minted as a non-transferable NFT to a trust entity on-chain — cryptographically bound to your verified identity and impossible to forge.</p>
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
